general.name: photoROSATCamcol
general.description: Match of objects in a camcol of the SDSS imaging catalog to the ROSAT All-Sky Survey Faint Source Catalogue and Bright Source Catalogue . These matches are to any objects which are RUN_PRIMARY according to the local resolve (see resolve documentation ). See individual field files for full description.
